{"tid":1672333,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[加泰問題] 真不割方法","createTime":"2019-10-24T04:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T05:24:33.000Z","uid":263176,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6401ce911370186578c1a3189c4f217a8918a916","tid":1672333,"uid":263176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:55:38.000Z","msg":"相信好多好多手足, <br />\n都已經睇左好多唔同嘅分析. <br />\n唔同嘅資料. <br />\n<br />\n點解去/ 唔去. <br />\n呢個POST 唔係叫大家去定唔去. <br />\n因為兄弟爬山, <br />\n<br />\n但其實唔應該各自努力. <br />\n我地都預會有手足去, <br />\n而唔去嘅大多擔心比人扣分裂主義, 港獨.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">手足去我地阻唔到, 就努力準備好外國文宣, <br />\n同議員, 外國民眾, 媒體去清楚解釋, </span></strong></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地集會係反對西班牙政府警暴, 同因政見而加害人民. <br />\n呢一個我地有共嗚, 係冇問題. 要少提加泰, 多提人權, 自由. </span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">外語文宣</span></span>, 唔係中文自己J. <br />\n<br />\n我地不分割, <br />\n就好似前線要衝, <br />\n阻唔到, 就幫手傳物資. <br />\n<br />\n因為我地係一家人, 一家人可以意見唔同, <br />\n但會互相幫助.<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">同時, 參加集會嘅, 一見有人叫支持加獨, <br />\n要大大力噓. </span></span></strong><br />\n有好多野, 安全至上, <br />\n大家都明, 講獨立, 百害而冇一利"},{"pid":"81f74e9b60109d2cd8611d1b4edf04a6dcb73713","tid":1672333,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T04:56:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCA3VqG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCA3VqG.jpg&h=1b492863&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a7293bbb7860943555378a974524582c8bb9cdad","tid":1672333,"uid":109589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T05:22:41.000Z","msg":"加泰玩共産<br />\n你同佢地係兄弟？"},{"pid":"506ced896ec4